Transformations:
1. X_test and y_test (append to) -> test. X_train and y_train (append to)-> train. 
2. test and train (merge) -> Alldata
3. Alldata (reshape) -> mAlldata
4. mAlldata (order) ->finalAlldata
5. finalAlldata (tapply) -> Mean and Sd
6. X_test, y_test and subject_test (append to) -> test. X_train, y_train and subject_train (append to)-> train.
7. test and train (merge) -> Alldata
8. Alldata (reshape) -> mAlldata
9. mAlldata (order) ->finalAlldata
10. finalAlldata (tapply) -> Mean for each subject and each measurement
